rule_name: bugs with (purple legs and white heads) or orange wings
text: The zorb with wings will only have orange wings. The other zorbs with legs will have white heads with purple legs and/or bodies.

rule_name: bugs with (purple legs and white heads) or orange wings
text: The other critters with white wings are not zorbs. If the critter has legs and a purple head, it is not a zorb.
